<subSubSection pageId="103" pageNumber="861" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="103.[1395,2606,711,1454]" pageId="103" pageNumber="861">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1397,1752,1303,1336]" pageId="103" pageNumber="861">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[1766,1819,1303,1336]" country="Cameroon" name="North" pageId="103" pageNumber="861">Not</collectingRegion>
assessed on The IUCN Red List. Apparently threatened by logging and wood harvesting, but due to the recent taxonomic reclassification, its conservation status and population trends have not yet been properly assessed.
</paragraph>
